	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />While I'm *pretty* sure PAL games won't run correctly on my NTSC system, will Japanese games (translated games) be able to run fine? Or perhaps both PAL and Japanese games can? Maybe there's a patch to make either Japanese or PAL games work? I'm not sure whether Japanese games are NTSC or PAL... I can't find any information on this looking it up on the internet, so thanks a lot! (might come across as a total newb here heheh)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
