	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Japanese games are NTSC. Like Jeroen said, what could prevent you from playing them is that there are Japan-only mappers that might not have been implemented on the PowerPak yet. You can try all the games you want, it will not break your NES or your PowerPak (AFAIK), some will work, some will not, there is no characteristic that excludes a whole territory.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
